Paper: hep-th/9812186

Date: 1998-12-21

Title: Yangians, finite W-algebras and the Non Linear Schrodinger hierarchy

Authors: M. Mintchev, E. Ragoucy, P. Sorba and Ph. Zaugg

Comments: LaTeX2e, 10 pages, Talk presented by E. Ragoucy at ACTP-Nankai

Symposium on Yang-Baxter systems, non linear models and their applications,Seoul (Korea) October 20-23, 1998Journal-ref: J.Phys. A32 (1999) 5885-5900

We show an algebra morphism between Yangians and some finite W-algebras. Thiscorrespondence is nicely illustrated in the framework of the Non LinearSchrodinger hierarchy. For such a purpose, we give an explicit realization ofthe Yangian generators in terms of deformed oscillators.